# Build Policy — Incremental Close-Out Build

**Status:** Project policy (2026-07). At the **end of every completed task** that touched compile inputs, run an **incremental** Release build. CMake/MSVC recompiles **only changed** `.cpp` / headers / touched units — not a full clean rebuild or vcpkg/qtbase reinstall.

See also: `.cursor/rules/no-full-rebuild.mdc` (hard bans on `cmake --preset` when `build/` exists).

## Task close (default — required when code changed)

| Do | Don't |
|----|-------|
| `.\scripts\build-release.ps1` at task close (only path for AI) | `cmake --preset default` when `build/CMakeCache.txt` exists |
| Re-use existing `build/` — changed sources only recompile | Raw `cmake --build` without `build-release.ps1` (skips lock recovery) |
| Kill `PIPBONG.exe` before link — `build-release.ps1` does this | Parallel cmake configure (IDE + script) |
| Run `cmake --preset default` **only** when `build/` is missing | Full clean rebuild unless user explicitly asks |
| Skip close-out build when task changed **only** docs / `.cursor/rules` / changelog with **no** C++/headers/`CMakeLists.txt` | Run build mid-implementation unless user asks or compile check needed |

**Command (mandatory for AI):** `.\scripts\build-release.ps1` from repo root.

**IDE / F5 (mandatory):** Ctrl+Shift+B builds; F5 runs **Build and Run** task only (no CodeLLDB) — see `.cursor/rules/f5-build-and-run.mdc`, `ide-build-workflow.mdc`, `no-full-rebuild.mdc`.

**Recovery if build hangs on vcpkg lock:** `.\scripts\recover-ide-build.ps1`

**Dev preset:** `PIPBONG_SKIP_WINDEPLOY=ON` — incremental links skip `windeployqt` (~3 s no-change / ~5–15 s single-file edits). Run `.\scripts\deploy-qt.ps1` once when DLLs beside the exe are missing.

A `CMakeLists.txt` **version bump** triggers CMake reconfigure and regenerates `PipbongVersion.h` — expect **only** `Application.cpp` + `UpdateChecker.cpp` to recompile (~seconds–1 min), **not** vcpkg/qtbase rebuild or every translation unit.

## Version bump close — mandatory backup + GitHub release

**Every version bump** (task close per AGENTS.md §10) **must** also:

| Step | Command |
|------|---------|
| Backup | `git add` (tracked files; not `build/`) → `git commit` → `git push origin main` on **`Baegovda/PIPBONG`** |
| Release | `.\scripts\create-github-release.ps1` — runs `package-release.ps1` → `build-release.ps1` (incremental) |

**Do not** finish a version-bump task with only local commits or without publishing the matching GitHub Release.

## Distribution packaging

| Script | When |
|--------|------|
| `.\scripts\package-release.ps1` | Called by `create-github-release.ps1`; ad-hoc local ZIP only if needed |
| `.\scripts\create-github-release.ps1` | **Mandatory** at every version-bump task close |

Ship the **ZIP** (exe + `PIPBONGUpdater.exe` + Qt/OpenCV DLLs). Users extract and run `PIPBONG.exe` from the folder.

## CMake preset

| Preset | Purpose |
|--------|---------|
| **`default`** | `x64-windows`, `build/`, dynamic DLL linking — **first configure only** |

